<br /><br />Upon hearing this, the woman decided to stay in the hospital and have a face lift, liposuction and a tummy tuck. She even had someone change her hair color. Since she had so much more time to live, she figured she might as well make the most of it. 
<br /><br />She was released from the hospital but while crossing the street on her way home, she was killed by a car. 
<br /><br />Arriving in front of God, she demanded, &quot;I thought you said I had another 43 years?! Why didn't you pull me out of the path of that car?&quot; 
