<br /><br />&quot;Oh, I don't know,&quot; said the stranger. &quot;How about nuclear power?&quot;
<br /><br />&quot;OK,&quot; said Little Johnny. &quot;That could be an interesting topic. But let me ask you a question first. &quot;A horse, a cow, and a deer all eat grass. The same stuff. Yet a deer excretes little pellets, while a cow turns out a flat patty, and a horse produces clumps of dried grass. Why do you suppose that is?&quot;
<br /><br />&quot;Jeez,&quot; said the stranger. &quot;I have no idea.&quot;
<br /><br />&quot;Well, then,&quot; said Little Johnny, &quot;How is it that you feel qualified to discuss nuclear power when you don't know shit?&quot;

